headline: A Fresh Look at Nasdaq (NDAQ) Valuation and Upside Potential
summary: Nasdaq (NDAQ) shares have moved sideways over the past week, with a slight dip in the month and the past 3 months. Investors are weighing these recent performance trends in comparison to steady long-term returns and improving net income. See our latest analysis for Nasdaq. Nasdaq’s share price recently cooled off after strong year-to-date gains, but its 1-year total shareholder return of 13.4% and robust five-year total return of 125% highlight its consistent ability to generate long-term...
